  "prompt": "Which are the top software companies in Ahmedabad for .net developers?",
  "response": "Ahmedabad, a growing IT hub in India, has several software companies that offer opportunities for **.NET developers**. Here are some of the top companies known for their work in .NET development:\n\n### 1. **TatvaSoft**\n   - A well-known software development company specializing in custom software solutions using technologies like .NET, Angular, and React.\n   - Offers end-to-end .NET development services for web and mobile applications.\n\n### 2. **Radixweb**\n   - A prominent IT services company providing .NET development, ERP solutions, and custom software development.\n   - Known for its expertise in ASP.NET, C#, and Microsoft technologies.\n\n### 3. **Simform**\n   - A leading software development and consulting company that works extensively with .NET for enterprise-level applications.\n   - Offers services in cloud computing, mobile app development, and custom software solutions.\n\n### 4. **Concetto Labs**\n   - A software development company specializing in .NET, PHP, and mobile app development.\n   - Known for building scalable and robust applications using Microsoft technologies.\n\n### 5. **Peerbits**\n   - A software development firm that provides .NET development services for web and mobile applications.\n   - Focuses on custom software, enterprise solutions, and cloud-based applications.\n\n### 6. **Elluminati Inc**\n   - A technology company offering .NET development services for web and mobile applications.\n   - Specializes in custom software development and IT consulting.\n\n### 7. **Hidden Brains**\n   - A software development company with expertise in .NET, AI, IoT, and blockchain technologies.\n   - Provides custom software solutions and enterprise application development.\n\n### 8. **Vrinsoft Technology**\n   - A software development company offering .NET development services for web and mobile applications.\n   - Specializes in custom software development and IT outsourcing.\n\n### 9. **Greeky Ants**\n   - A software development company focusing on .NET, PHP, and mobile app development.\n   - Known for building scalable and user-friendly applications.\n\n### 10. **Brainvire**\n   - A global IT consulting and software development company with expertise in .NET, eCommerce, and AI solutions.\n   - Provides custom software development and enterprise solutions.\n\nThese companies are actively hiring .NET developers and provide opportunities to work on diverse projects. If you're a .NET developer looking for opportunities in Ahmedabad, these companies are worth exploring.",
